# Render with: vhs demo.tape  (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs)
Output demo.gif
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme { "background": "#212337", "foreground": "#ebfafa" }

Type "ritual status" Enter Sleep 2s
Type "ritual findings" Enter Sleep 2s
Type "ritual" Enter Sleep 3s
Type ":" Sleep 1s
Type "run plan" Sleep 2s
Escape Sleep 1s
Type "?" Sleep 2s
Escape
Type "q" Sleep 1s
